data.description:
Florida living at it's finest! In this beautiful 3 Bedroom 3 Bathroom w/den & 2 car garage townhome in the desirable Pointe West Community. Open concept, stainless steel appliances, natural gas. Dine on the patio off the kitchen. Master boasts large en-suite bath & spacious walk in closet. Enjoy the community pool, playground and shaded sidewalks. HOA includes roof, yard work, and exterior maintenance. New roof 2023,
A/C 2023. Sizes approx - subj to error.
